headline.print_headline: Haiti Leader Accepts Report Calling for New Gov't
headline.main: Haiti Leader Accepts Report Calling for New Gov't

lead_paragraph: President Michel Martelly said Friday night that he accepted all the findings of a report this week from a government-appointed commission, including its recommendation that the prime minister resign.
